這是一個專門用於 Debian 12 的精簡版腳本，僅保留禁用核心更新的功能。
它結合了 apt-mark hold（鎖定當前版本）與 APT Pinning（禁止所有未來內核安裝）雙重保護。
bash
#!/bin/bash

# Check root privileges
if [ "$EUID" -ne 0 ]; then 
  echo "Error: Please run as root or using sudo."
  exit 1
fi

echo "--- Disabling Kernel Updates for Debian 12 ---"

# 1. Lock the current running kernel packages
CURRENT_KERNEL=$(uname -r)
# Find related image, headers, and modules
KERNEL_PKGS=$(dpkg -l | grep -E "linux-image-$CURRENT_KERNEL|linux-headers-$CURRENT_KERNEL|linux-modules-$CURRENT_KERNEL" | awk '{print $2}')

if [ -n "$KERNEL_PKGS" ]; then
    apt-mark hold $KERNEL_PKGS
    echo "Success: The following packages are now on hold:"
    echo "$KERNEL_PKGS"
else
    echo "Warning: Could not find specific packages for kernel $CURRENT_KERNEL"
fi

# 2. Create APT preference to block all future kernel-related installations
cat <<EOF > /etc/apt/preferences.d/no-kernel-upgrades
Package: linux-image-* linux-headers-* linux-kbuild-* linux-modules-*
Pin: release *
Pin-Priority: -1
EOF

echo "Success: APT Pinning created at /etc/apt/preferences.d/no-kernel-upgrades"
echo "--------------------------------------------------"
echo "Kernel updates are now completely DISABLED."
echo "To verify, run: apt-mark showhold"
echo "--------------------------------------------------"
请谨慎使用此类代码。
腳本說明：
apt-mark hold: 防止 apt upgrade 更新目前已安裝的內核套件。
Pin-Priority: -1: 這是最高級別的禁止，即使有新版本的內核出現在軟體源中，apt 也會完全忽略它們。
如果您未來需要恢復更新，只需刪除 /etc/apt/preferences.d/no-kernel-upgrades 檔案並執行 sudo apt-mark unhold 即可。


